title: Destined Murderer
summary: Destined Murderer Manhwa “I can see your number. The number of people you will kill in the future.” If he kills before they kill, the murder will not occur. Serial killer, Number, punishes the ‘Destined Murderers’ one at a time under that resolution. Could his wish to create a world without murder through murder ever be accomplished? 살인예정자, The Murderer
